column1:
look for kind hearted.....have a great respect to all mankind.
I'm looking for someone I appreciate and appreciates me.i hate liars. i can't stand them.

Comunication- You need to be able to talk to your partner and trust that they will take into consideration you thoughts and opinions. If your relationship lacks this one simple quality, then you may as well be kissing a brick wall.

Comprimise- Both partners need to be able to give a little. One reason I believe alot of relationships fail is because one or both partners are selfish and want things their way.

Common goals- It is important to discuss with you partner things such as plans for your life, and wether or not you want children. 

Loyalty- It is VERY important to find someone who believes in commitment and will be loyal to you in marrige or in any relationship.

Love- There is a difference between Infatuation and Love. Dont let your heart get in the way of your mind and reason. Give it time to mature and dont hgo making any long term commitments until your sure that what your feeling is real.Be sure that you partner is will to do the same.


Humor- I love to laugh, and I love people who make me laugh.

There also has to be respect, consideration, and an ear or two to listen with.,"Strength of character,confident,Honesty &  integrity. Trust faith, sense of humor.
